Agents of the All Progress Congress, APC, were caught thumb printing ballot papers at the party’s logo spot on behalf of voters  and passing  on the ballot to another party agent in drop in the  appropriate polling box at the  Kamanda Polling Unit 002  in Wammako local government area, Sokoto State.

Sokoto was said to have recorded large turnout of women voters  at the polling units as early as  8.35am.
Governor Aminu Waziri Tambuwal of Sokoto State was said to have cast his ballot at 11.42am at his Ward 011 Kofar Ajiya, Tambuwal local government area





